73,IssueCommentEvent,2017-03-21 16:13:25+00:00,55258005,jopohl/urh,18283204,andynoack,,,215226510,288130827,"rtl_tcp is quite simple, it sends samples after you have connected to the process. No matter, whether your configurations are completed or not. However, when wiretapping the communication with wireshark you can see that the sample transmission normally begins after all settings were done (due to a very fast configuration of all settings).
