2032,IssueCommentEvent,2018-04-27 23:06:05+00:00,94554082,dylanaraps/pywal,6799467,dylanaraps,,,318396384,385115423,"Here's the script I used to fix the values if you're interested.

```sh
#!/usr/bin/env bash
mkdir ~/col.out

for file in *.json; do
    jq "".colors.color9  = .colors.color1 |\
        .colors.color10 = .colors.color2 |\
        .colors.color11 = .colors.color3 |\
        .colors.color12 = .colors.color4 |\
        .colors.color13 = .colors.color5 |\
        .colors.color14 = .colors.color6"" ""$file"" > ~/col.out/""${file##*/}""
done
```",{},OWNER,User,False
