3862,IssueCommentEvent,2015-10-30 01:17:53+00:00,4882836,casebeer/python-hkdf,543934,doublereedkurt,,,112061321,152373341,"Shoot, I'm sorry I should have specified -- I'm not the project author just another user who is interested.

That is an interesting use case.  The generated password needs to not only be random, but also look random to a human.  (Or, sacrifice a minimal amount of true randomness for apparent randomness.)

