6433,IssueCommentEvent,2017-12-19 06:13:28+00:00,82026170,emlynoregan/appenginetaskutils,985549,emlynoregan,,,279842189,352649929,"Ok, I've added a new function, ""set_taskroute"", for this. You need to call it before you set up your routes. In your main.py or equivalent (wherever you set up the ""app"" object for your app):

Flask:

from taskutils import set_taskroute
set_taskroute(""/customtask"")
