7072,IssueCommentEvent,2017-09-18 16:51:12+00:00,34864402,apache/incubator-mxnet,11234557,cjolivier01,47359,apache,258264181,330284076,"**Looks like problem was introduced here**  
https://github.com/apache/incubator-mxnet/commit/0b1363116c84dcefa751a925749b2da04c3f2614

**In function** 
void FillZerosCsrImpl(mshadow::Stream<xpu> *s, NDArray *dst)

**Why?**
CSR matrix, even if all ""zeros"", must have m + 1 items in its row pointer (csr::IndPtr) array.  Current implementation leaves all aux arrays empty.

**PR of fix**
https://github.com/apache/incubator-mxnet/pull/7935
",{},CONTRIBUTOR,User,False
