8987,IssueCommentEvent,2015-02-11 16:31:35+00:00,19387849,Parsely/streamparse,136574,kbourgoin,779641,Parsely,56260361,73912440,"I'm pretty sure the root cause is in here:  https://github.com/Parsely/streamparse/blob/master/streamparse/bolt.py#L134-L147

