9110,IssueCommentEvent,2015-05-10 20:49:03+00:00,2014929,scikit-image/scikit-image,263366,emmanuelle,897180,scikit-image,74740449,100699594,"Thank you Matthew! It's certainly interesting to know that there exists BSD code for Euler characteristic written by a specialist like Jonathan Taylor. We might need someone more knowledgeable about Euler characteristic to join the discussion: ``scikit-image`` code implements an intuitive definition of the Euler characteristic  (counting the number of holes as defined by a structuring element), that might differ from the result of the definition used in polyhedral combinatorics. Not sure that this is a problem, but this should be at least documented. Or we could have the two implementations, depending on accuracy and performance.",{},,User,False
