         path @loader_path/. (offset 12)
```

What this means is that the package will try to load library `@rpath/libomp.dylib`, where `@rpath` is defined as `@loader_path/.`. Thus, the library is loaded from `@loader_path/libomp.dylib`, where `@loader_path` is the path of `_datatable.cpython-37m-darwin.so`.",{},MEMBER,User,False
