10640,IssueCommentEvent,2016-04-20 10:11:09+00:00,48182096,appnexus/pyrobuf,977633,onesuper,1664176,appnexus,149377198,212364521,"Hi Greg

Thank you for your quick reply! I have copied and pasted a code piece generated by pyrobuf (for the integer test). It looks as if  int32/int64 will use set_signed_varint  and get_signed_varint to serialize/deserialize values.

```
        while current_offset < size:
            key = get_varint64(memory, &current_offset)
            field_idx = (key >> 3)
            # wire_type = (key & 0x7)
            # Int64
            if field_idx == 1:
                self._Int64_isSet = True
                self._Int64 = get_signed_varint64(memory, &current_offset)
            # Int32
            elif field_idx == 2:
                self._Int32_isSet = True
                self._Int32 = get_signed_varint32(memory, &current_offset)
            # UInt64
            elif field_idx == 3:
                self._UInt64_isSet = True
                self._UInt64 = get_varint64(memory, &current_offset)
            # UInt32
            elif field_idx == 4:
                self._UInt32_isSet = True
                self._UInt32 = get_varint32(memory, &current_offset)
            # SInt64
            elif field_idx == 5:
                self._SInt64_isSet = True
                self._SInt64 = get_signed_varint64(memory, &current_offset)
            # SInt32
            elif field_idx == 6:
                self._SInt32_isSet = True
                self._SInt32 = get_signed_varint32(memory, &current_offset)
```

```
    cdef void _protobuf_serialize(self, bytearray buf):
        cdef int key
        cdef int field_idx
        cdef int wire_type

        # Int64
        if self._Int64_isSet:
            field_idx = 1
            wire_type = 0
            key = (field_idx << 3) | wire_type
            set_varint64(key, buf)
	    set_signed_varint64(self._Int64, buf)

        # Int32
        if self._Int32_isSet:
	    field_idx = 2
            wire_type = 0
            key = (field_idx << 3) | wire_type
            set_varint64(key, buf)
            set_signed_varint32(self._Int32, buf)

	# UInt64
```


Cheers,
Greg",{},,User,False
