13082,IssueCommentEvent,2017-10-14 01:58:32+00:00,6235174,conda/conda,1418419,kalefranz,6392739,conda,265420593,336601921,"Another datapoint, I tried conda 4.4.0rc1, manually adding pkgs/main to `defaults` (it's not merged up yet for 4.4.0rc1, it will be included in 4.4.0rc2).  It segfaulted on me twice, and then proceeded as expected, *without* changing the python version.  Interesting.

