(set-option :smt.delay_units_threshold 16)
(set-option :type_check true)
(set-option :smt.bv.reflect true)
(set-option :smt.timeout 10000)
```

The sort/function declarations and assertions (this was obtained by using solver.toString()) are:
```
(declare-datatypes () ((General (G_Boolean (of_G_Boolean Bool)) (G_Integer (of_G_Integer Int)) (G_String (of_G_String String)) (G_Null))))
