16471,IssueCommentEvent,2017-08-29 11:51:51+00:00,10040793,scrapy-plugins/scrapy-splash,932835,rlucca,13627237,scrapy-plugins,129678916,325640047,"It is returning a fail inside the generator, it is not being treat possibly because you doesnt specified an errback function. Just try change:

   yield scrapy.Request(url, self.parse_item, meta={'splash': ...})

To:

   yield scrapy.Request(url, self.parse_item, errback=self.parse_error, meta={'splash': ...})

This should call your self.parse_error.",{},,User,False
