16594,IssueCommentEvent,2017-06-10 00:16:12+00:00,43023379,hackingmaterials/atomate,7681751,bocklund,14116185,hackingmaterials,234955020,307528479,"What do you think about moving the YAML to its own tutorial not on the main track? I think it's useful to see if you really want a YAML file. If a user wanted to make a workflow, they would want to do so because their calculation is non-trivial and all of the existing workflow YAML files are nice and short, but trivial. 

