16647,IssueCommentEvent,2016-06-03 20:17:28+00:00,43852872,PulpQE/pulp-smash,1012989,Ichimonji10,14839747,PulpQE,158136990,223683442,"When implementing this test, consider taking a look at https://repos.fedorapeople.org/pulp/pulp/fixtures/rpm/repodata/. If you open and decompress the `...-updateinfo.xml.gz` file, you'll see this:

```xml
