- DockerTestPackageRunner.run() would trigger to download the same image 5 times
- Starting 5 containers (if we add a random string to the docker container name)
- install/upgrade conan_package_tools and conan in each container
- commit each container layer to the same docker image and delete the random container

In our environment we already provide a docker image which includes conan_package_tools and conan and so we only need the pull image part of the run method

