17554,IssueCommentEvent,2017-09-17 23:08:59+00:00,26516210,certbot/certbot,5235109,joohoi,17889013,certbot,202822398,330100585,"This PR contains a lot of things I'm building on, and it's a nice overall cleanup of the configurator, hence: Ready for yet another round of review :)

